'The wood must be collected from the Galtrev Lumber-camp once again, but everyone is afraid to go out with the Dragon-clan roaming about unhindered.\n\n'You have proven a worthy opponent to their numbers, Duvodiad. Will you go bring today's wood delivery to Galtrev?'
The Galtrev Lumber-camp is not far to the north of Galtrev.\n\nWood is needed from the Galtrev Lumber-camp, but the threat of Dragon-clan thieves have made delivery a problem.
'You are a valuable asset to our village, [placeholder]! Thank you again...I know this must be a chore for you, but you help us greatly with tasks such as these.'
Fraid is near the overturned waggon on the outskirts of the Galtrev Lumber-camp.\n\nYou should bring the wood you gathered to Fraid.
The wood you collected is in a pile near the overturned waggon.\n\nYou have recovered some wood and should now carry it to Galtrev.
'It would be nice not to have to worry about these shipments once in a while.'
'Ah, well done. Let us bundle these into one shipment that you can carry to Macsen.'
Macsen is in Galtrev.\n\nYou should speak with Macsen to complete your daily delivery of the wood shipment from the Galtrev Lumber-camp.
